{"tid":1844822,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"長時間帶口罩帶得耐既缺點","createTime":"2020-01-26T20:07:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T07:39:56.000Z","uid":223892,"like":10,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"a8833806e37661d38dcedc43925f4558635ce297","tid":1844822,"uid":223892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T20:07:57.000Z","msg":"本人2X歲，都同大部分人一樣經歷過SARS<br />\n知道口罩既重要性<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無記錯個陣時無論出街定係屋企都日日帶住個marks<br />\n講緊係最普通個隻3層marks<br />\n帶左唔記得幾多日之後<br />\n發覺心口唔知點解愈黎愈痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個陣仲好驚唔係呀嘛咁都中<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後睇左幾個醫生都話無野<br />\n依稀記得其中有個醫生問我係咪長時間帶住個marks<br />\n我就話一日帶7-8個鐘<br />\n之後個醫生就呆左同我講有d地方就唔洗帶<br />\n平常人帶4到5個鐘<br />\n如果長期帶住會影響肺工能<br />\n反而對個肺唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當然我唔係鼓吹大家啦唔洗帶口罩啦<br />\n但一定要睇住自己身體<br />\n有唔舒服既就更加要帶同埋睇醫生<br />\n最後小弟祝各位身體健康，心想事成<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32adcb30742482d9936810892148d8d4b433ced0","tid":1844822,"uid":55309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T20:09:55.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"b24b801a34562341df30b9c8ca4fa90304244d52","tid":1844822,"uid":7854,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T20:11:54.000Z","msg":"室內就一定要囉<br />\n<br />\n室外睇清況  唔係好密集人既唔洗都得既"},{"pid":"76de631da4e3143184b4e3f69d174ca3c18066e0","tid":1844822,"uid":155818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T20:11:55.000Z","msg":"我做野都長戴...<br />\n根本無可能4-5個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d9ccdddf207d3e4561b8aaa4c15639fa55ad184","tid":1844822,"uid":9,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T20:12:52.000Z","msg":"塊面會痛,鐵線個位"},{"pid":"4ad8392b13a165f087da289a2857e8c02ba62e6c","tid":1844822,"uid":223892,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b24b801a34562341df30b9c8ca4fa90304244d52","tid":1844822,"uid":7854,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T20:11:54.000Z","msg":"室內就一定要囉<br />\n<br />\n室外睇清況  唔係好密集人既唔洗都得既"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T20:14:29.000Z","msg":"個陣係學校上堂，無辦法唔長期帶<br />\n最恐怖係個陣成日比人灌輸你唔帶個marks就一定會中招<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e37530656467428af3d6f9c6b905b9ffae27afaa","tid":1844822,"uid":105271,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T20:15:43.000Z","msg":"搽完cream/化咗妝戴mask 塊面會起粒粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個問由10月到依家都解決唔到 唯有出少d街"},{"pid":"fefb01e251ac828c7225038da9baa6cd3e367616","tid":1844822,"uid":223892,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"76de631da4e3143184b4e3f69d174ca3c18066e0","tid":1844822,"uid":155818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T20:11:55.000Z","msg":"我做野都長戴...<br />\n根本無可能4-5個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T20:15:53.000Z","msg":"我好明白<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但人一驚就會逼自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44a1823c1015add8f029a684ef3fee0eff1dcd9a","tid":1844822,"uid":105271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e37530656467428af3d6f9c6b905b9ffae27afaa","tid":1844822,"uid":105271,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-2